й системы Windows или Linux в Балашихе.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-10-16 00:48:52', '2023-10-16 00:48:52', '2023-10-16 00:48:52', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 15, 19, 18, NULL, 1, NULL);
